**__Our Encyclopedia's mission__**
In creating this server, we came in with two main goals. 

> **__To create a collection of up to date, quality guides for every boss in RuneScape. __**
⬥ We are completely open source. Completion of #772256355380887634 grants access to our Guide Writing channels. Thus such objectiv is achieved through community effort from our <@622103061875130388> and <@724127532445859863> collaborators. 
⬥ In mantaining our objective alive, we constantly seek out Editors who are willing to lend a hand with writing our Encylopaedia. New guides are nearly always welcome. 


⬥ To create an environment where questions can be given quality answers. Don't be shy, we're here to help!
